'''Freedom Arms''' is a Freedom, [[Wyoming]]-based firearm manufacturing company, known for producing powerful single-action [[revolver]]s.  The company was founded in 1983 by Dick Casull to produce a revolver chambered in the powerful [[.454 Casull]] chambering.  This 5-shot revolver was the Model 83.

